<Link id="l00029" /><CodeLine lineNumber="29"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// For example, it might render as &#96;DEADBEEFCAFEBABE&#96; (YAML does not</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00034" /><CodeLine lineNumber="34"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// For example, all of the following are acceptable:</span></CodeLine>
